text: The women's individual competition of the Golf events at the 2019 Pan American Games was held between August 8 and 11 at the Country Club Villa in Lima, Peru. Amateur Emilia Migliaccio won the gold medal for the United States. ==Schedule== All times are PET (UTC−5). {| class="wikitable" ! Date ! Time !
